             <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 md:p-8">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-2 text-[#003B71]">Mastering Your Attentional Focus</h2>
                <p class="text-center text-gray-600 max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-8">Elite performance requires shifting your focus dynamically. Concentration is not about blocking everything out; it's about focusing on the right thing at the right time.</p>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                    
                    <div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 border-t-4 border-[#00A1E4]">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-center text-[#0073BC]">Broad External</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-center text-gray-600">Used to rapidly assess a situation. (e.g., A quarterback scanning the field).</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 border-t-4 border-[#00A1E4]">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-center text-[#0073BC]">Narrow External</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-center text-gray-600">Used to focus on one or two external cues. (e.g., Focusing only on the ball).</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 border-t-4 border-[#00A1E4]">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-center text-[#0073BC]">Broad Internal</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-center text-gray-600">Used to analyze a plan or strategy without external input. (e.g., A coach reviewing a game plan).</p>
                    </div>
                     <div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 border-t-4 border-[#00A1E4]">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-center text-[#0073BC]">Narrow Internal</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-center text-gray-600">Used to mentally rehearse a skill or control emotions. (e.g., A diver visualizing a dive).</p>
